form.current-chamber: IN THE SENATE OF THE UNITED STATES

action.action-desc: Mr. Reid (for himself and Mr. McConnell) submitted the following resolution; which was considered and agreed to

form.official-title: Notifying the President of the United States of the election of a Sergeant at Arms and Doorkeeper of the Senate.

section.text: That the President of the United States be notified of the election of the Honorable Andrew B. Willison as Sergeant at Arms and Doorkeeper of the Senate.
